OL,3,CWhat we know about water contamination
OL,4,Cas parasite sparks mass illness
OL,6,FAn outbreak of a diarrhoea and
OL,7,Fvomiting illness in south Devon has
OL,8,Fseen thousands of people told to boil
OL,9,Ftheir tap water before using it until
OL,10,Ffurther notice.
OL,12,FDozens of people in Brixham have been
OL,13,Ftaken ill and a school has been closed
OL,14,Fdue to the issue.
OL,16,FThe UK Health Security Agency has so
OL,17,Ffar confirmed 22 cases of the parasite
OL,18,F- but as many as 70 more have been
OL,19,Ftaken ill.
