OL,6,F"I'm disgusted really," one resdient
OL,7,Fsaid. "Everyone in our street has
OL,8,Fsomeone poorly in their household."
OL,10,FRipley Couzens said the whole
OL,11,Fsituation is "ridiculous" but that
OL,12,F"the community is coming together" as
OL,13,Fa result of the problems.
OL,15,FAron Davis has a young son who is
OL,16,Fdiabetic, which means he is very
OL,17,Freliant on water. He said they were
OL,18,Fwaiting overnight for a delivery of
OL,19,Fbottled water.
