OL,6,FMr Davis said: "I think it's
OL,7,Fdiabolical, absolutely diabolical.
OL,9,F"We had a system where we boiled the
OL,10,Fwater as we were advised. We followed
OL,11,Fthe instructions for it to cool down,
OL,12,Fleft it, tasted it, got sick from the
OL,13,Ftaste of it."
OL,15,FAshley Hamilton owns The Curious
OL,16,FKitchen. He said it's "been a bit of a
OL,17,Fshock" and they're now empty.
OL,19,FHe said they are changing their
OL,20,Fcleaning processes, and "being extra
OL,21,Fextra cautious".
