OL,6,FMr Hamilton said: "We're a tourist
OL,7,Ftown, coming into the busiest time of
OL,8,Fthe year - so it's worrying."
OL,10,FMary Alwood is from Brixham Fruit
OL,11,FSupplies. They're stacking up hundreds
OL,12,Fof bottles of water outside the shop
OL,13,Ffor people to take for free, and
OL,14,Fnoting down addresses they can deliver
OL,15,Fto.
OL,17,FShe said one of her elderly deaf
OL,18,Fneighbours was sat out all day waiting
OL,19,Ffor a water delivery that never came.
