OL,6,F'She was waiting all day for her water
OL,7,Fto be delivered'
OL,9,FMs Alwood said: "It's been manic. We
OL,10,Fwant to help as many people as we can.
OL,12,F"We're inundated with messages,
OL,13,Fthere's so many elderly vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople that have no water."
