OL,6,FHowever, year six children were asked
OL,7,Fto attend the school for their final
OL,8,FSATs paper and take drinking water
OL,9,Fwith them.
OL,11,FIn a statement, a school spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "Despite repeated calls to South
OL,13,FWest Water about the urgency of the
OL,14,Fsituation, the school has not received
OL,15,Fany bottled water or assurances of
OL,16,Fwhen water will be delivered."
OL,18,FThe school says it remains hopeful it
OL,19,Fcan reopen on Friday 17 May and will
OL,20,Fprovide an update to parents on
OL,21,FThursday.
