OL,6,FWhat has South West Water said?
OL,8,FSouth West Water says it is working
OL,9,Fclosely with the UK Health Security
OL,10,FAgency and public health partners to
OL,11,F"urgently investigate" how
OL,12,Fcryptosporidium is getting into its
OL,13,Fnetwork so it can be fixed.
OL,15,FThe firm's chief customer and digital
OL,16,Fofficer Laura Flowerdew said: "We
OL,17,Fsincerely apologise for the impact
OL,18,Fthis is having on our customers in the
OL,19,FBrixham and Alston areas.
