OL,6,F"Protecting the health of our
OL,7,Fcustomers and providing them with a
OL,8,Fclean, fresh drinking water supply is
OL,9,Four number one priority and we will
OL,10,Fcontinue to work around the clock to
OL,11,Fmake sure that happens as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible."
OL,14,FSarah Bird, consultant in health
OL,15,Fprotection at UKHSA South West said:
OL,16,F"We advise people in the affected
OL,17,Fareas to follow the advice from South
OL,18,FWest Water and boil their drinking
OL,19,Fwater and allow to cool before use.
